title.rendered: Titus Tub Chair – end of line

content.rendered:
The Titus Tub Chair is made from our standard high quality, in house faux leather and a solid beech frame. Made in the EU.

Perfect for commercial venues such as bars, pubs and clubs but can also be used in offices and alike.

The Titus Tub Chair is available in an array of colours, for delivery in 2-4 working days. 2 year warranty. This price is whilst stocks last.
